{
  "stem": "23942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If my common sense said this, you don't do, you don't do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I used my first common sense that came into my head.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I realized going on that road that on one hand I could have maybe a sort of-- I could have a bed and place and some food, but I didn't want to be killed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I didn't want to take the chance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because I made up my mind, I'm going to survive at all odds.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I wasn't going to do anything that's comfortable at the moment, but I wasn't going to be killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And nobody's going to have a chance to find out who I am to be killed, OK?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I decided to take my chances the way I survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I walked back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I remember that day very clearly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I didn't take her offer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had a few offers like this, but I didn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One way or the other, somebody-- I was always afraid that if I stay one place, somehow the Germans will get a hold of that I am hiding.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I didn't want to give them that chance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I decided I'll be one step ahead of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, I figured a way that I will survive this way, not-- you know, not by hiding or having a comfortable home and then be caught or whatever.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that's how I survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this Lady Gdynska was kind.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But in her way she was so religious.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She thought-- she was taught that you save a soul, a Jewish soul, by trying to either to baptize me or to make me into a Catholic like her.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she did have her reason for wanting me to become nun.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
